text: Gildo Lourenço Vilanculos (born 31 January 1995) is a Mozambican professional footballer who plays as a winger for Marítimo B. ==Football career== Gildo Vilanculos started is professional career on the Mozambican club Ferroviário. On 10 January 2017, Gildo signed a four-and-a-half contract with Marítimo. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1995 births Category:People from Beira, Mozambique Category:Living people Category:Mozambican footballers Category:Association football wingers Category:Clube Ferroviário da Beira players Category:Mozambique international footballers Category:C.S.
